---
# Semver of @big-calendar/react in use.
version: "1.20.0"

# Which calendar views to enable.
# Options: month | week | work_week | day | agenda
views:
  - month
  - week
  - day
  - agenda

# Which features are active in this integration.
# Options: dnd | selection | resources
features:
  - dnd
  - selection

# Maps Big Calendar accessor keys to field names on your event/resource objects.
# Only the keys you need — omit the ones you don't use.
accessors:
  id: id                    # event.id — stable identity
  title: name               # event.name — display title
  start: startDate          # event.startDate — ISO 8601 datetime string
  end: endDate              # event.endDate — ISO 8601 datetime string
  allDay: isAllDay          # event.isAllDay — boolean
  # tooltip: description    # event.description — hover tooltip (optional)
  # resource: resourceId    # event.resourceId — link event to a resource
  # resourceId: id          # resource.id
  # resourceTitle: label    # resource.label
---

## App context

This project is a scheduling app for a medical practice. Events represent appointments.

**Data fetching:** Events are fetched from the REST API at `/api/appointments?start=&end=`.
The `onRangeChange` callback triggers a fetch whenever the visible window changes.

**Event editing:** We use shadcn/ui's `<Dialog>` component for editing appointments.
Clicking an event opens the dialog with the appointment pre-loaded.

**Creating events:** Slot selection (`onSlotSelect`) opens the same dialog with the
selected time range pre-filled.

**DnD:** Drag-to-move is enabled. We use optimistic updates — the local state is
updated immediately, and we roll back if the server save fails.

**Localizer:** `LuxonLocalizer` with `timeZone: 'America/New_York'`.
